Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:07.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 你说的那个城市还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就快到了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:11.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:20.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}话说回来 本该和贝尔两人单独约会的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:28.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么会变成这么大一帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}像我们一样 怪物们也能来到这一层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}与其说第18层是属于我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:58.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实更准确说是属于怪物们的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:03.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人 世界真美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}欢迎 同行们？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:53.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这里是里维拉 冒险者们建造的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好 好贵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:06.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个磨刀石居然卖13000巴利斯？太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:10.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个破背包也要20000 也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不要的话 我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这里的旅店也贵得离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以我们才在森林里扎营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咦 神明大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的 什么时候跑那儿去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这不是酒馆里那个菜鸟小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你丫的那时候居然敢……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:46.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂 莫尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你认识剑姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那些家伙 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你看 觉得这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:25.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}很香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吧是吧 我就知道贝尔会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:34.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在这种黑店城市买这种东西 太没经济观念了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}支援者不也买了个背包嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是回到地面的必需品 无奈之举
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这当然也是我的需要 这是作为少女的修养
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 你也不喜欢一身汗臭的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我倒从来没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:59.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫斯缇雅大人 我们商量一会儿去冲凉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的吗 我去 我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请务必带上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好 那大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}干什么 荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 回到营地以后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}伯特 真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:31.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是的 以后别让我干运送解毒药这苦差事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多亏你 明天可以全员出发回地面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}预定分成两组 你去先行组…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么那个胆小鬼会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}很多事是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个…荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}您说想两个人单独 我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么要爬树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}跟我上来就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}往下看 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看来是我压倒性的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你比个什么劲儿 赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:25.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}女孩们在冲凉 当然必须要偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}必须个鬼 荷米斯大人 不能干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 偷窥是属于男人的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 偷窥是属于男人的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们回去吧 荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咦 Argonaut君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么怎么 你也来冲凉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一脸老实相 你还挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:08.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实…其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}您在干什么 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:36.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咦 这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这下该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有水声？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:33.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}原来如此 我明白事情原委了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你不必放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:40.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我就这么原谅我了？ 不怕我说谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:45.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生 谦虚虽说是一种美德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:48.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但奉劝你还是别干贬低自己的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是你的坏毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:09:01.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呃…虽然有点晚 但还是谢谢你特意赶来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而且来这么危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:09.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不用在意 其实最近我也打算来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:34.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为了给她们献花 我偶尔会向米娅大妈请假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:37.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐 这里是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.06,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我曾经所属眷族的同伴们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:47.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}被与我们势不两立的对手在地下城算计
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:51.82,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}除我之外的队员 全都惨遭毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生 愿意听我的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我的名字已被登记在工会黑名单上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}因为我消灭了敌对眷族的全部人员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:20.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}偷袭 突袭 陷阱 为了替同伴报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我不择手段 被仇恨蒙蔽了双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}最后我精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对所有敌人报仇雪恨之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}倒在空无一人的阴暗后巷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:42.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这样的下场非常适合干下蠢事的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:43.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以 你被“丰饶的女主人”…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:58.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的 米娅大妈是在知道一切后接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}浪费你的时间听这些不堪的往事 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:10.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以我就是这样一个不知羞耻和残忍的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}让克朗尼先生失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐 还是不要干贬低自己的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这真是… 算是领教一回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 我说了不知天高地厚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生 你心地善良
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是一位值得我尊敬的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}脾气上来了 莫尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:10.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那臭小子是用什么骗术 来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}居然还敢神气活现的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么 你嫉妒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别以为与你们自己无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:25.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}初出茅庐的黄毛小子一升级马上来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:29.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}数年前就开始待在这里的我们成为笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:33.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}冒险者有属于冒险者的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们有义务教教他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}只要能诱他单独出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.60,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:52.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你这个胆小鬼 偏偏敢偷窥艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:56.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}臭小子 连我也不敢做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别吵了 这件事已经查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:02.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}荷米斯是罪魁祸首 真相已经水落石出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}放我下来 蠢双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:10.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个胆小鬼为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}说够了吧 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝小姐 差不多要出发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 我被安排在先发团队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们和后续团队一起出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呃…路上请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.79,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你也要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明明应该趁只有我一人入浴时出现的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咦 神明大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:33.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}未完少年 女神在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:39.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}若想救她 单独来中央树正东面的一本水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们居然敢做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别看我这样 到底还算是神明 你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你家的神明大人平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也不会干伤害女神这样遭报应的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么你是冲我来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:26.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}放心吧 我不会让他们出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:30.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在起将是我与你的生死决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:31.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错 很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}输的一方必须服从胜出一方的任何要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:42.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我赢的话 把你的全副身家交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:46.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果我赢的话 请把神明大人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:48.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但别会错意了 黄毛小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:56.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是一场虐杀你的好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:01.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}人不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}揍扁他 莫尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}把这猖狂的小子狠揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错 快点滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:27.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是备受期待的新手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快看那张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:37.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}魔法道具 Hades head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那玩意儿不赖嘛 亚丝菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是恶俗的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你对贝尔·克朗尼有仇不成？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}倒不如说这是我对他的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:52.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔对人类的丑恶一面了解甚少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:58.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不管趣味是否恶俗 只希望他知道人类的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不过我也不否认带一点看笑话的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}倘若他在此一蹶不振？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:08.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么正好说明他不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}咦 他们好像也发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他们中任何一人都很耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哪来的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔应该就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}卑鄙的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是未完少年的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.79,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么他们会知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别管这些 先消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}千草 拿枪来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哎呀 好热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶 我也想去热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}喂 不许无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}回荡于午夜十二时的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}支援者 你怎么知道我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}用了犬人的嗅觉能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:21.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多亏了赫斯缇雅大人乱花钱买的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}燃尽吧 外法之业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.05,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}混账
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶 这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不要怕 我们人数占上风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}包围他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶 无法靠近贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看来你们还是屡教不改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我来帮你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:28.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}臭小子 你看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能感觉到 充满敌意的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.41,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:25.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你这臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:28.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}孩子们 收起你们的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}哎呀 赫斯缇雅解放神威了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}今天的余兴节目结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 看到你没事 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:24.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:26.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}都是因为我 害你被打得这么满身是伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:35.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 是我没能保护好神明大人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这件事总算是结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}地震吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.05,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是… 不祥的摇晃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:50.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快看 那是什么
